facts.fact_text: The total gross disbursement of official development assistance for technical cooperation in constant prices of 2018 increased from 3.1 million dollars in 2000 to 14.1 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, most-favoured-nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with most-favoured-nation status declined from 22.4 % in 2005 to 5.6% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with preferential status declined from 22.4 % in 2005 to 5.6% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, most-favored nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average most-favored nation status tariff applied by developed countries declined from 5.2 % in 2000 to 4.2% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average preferential status tariff applied by developed countries was 2.6 % in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Dollar value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries (dollars)
facts.fact_text: The value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries was 21296.7 dollars in 2017.
